summary: This mod adds three new rooms to the Sky Haven Temple via a new door.
descriptionHtml:
UPDATE September 16, 2013 (from brokendeck)

Version 1.01 released.
- Navmesh fixed so followers will now follow you into every room of this mod.
- Couple more light fixes.

Be sure to check out the mod \"Sky Haven Temple More\" by brokendeck as well. It\'s perfectly compatible with this mod and can be found at http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/41626//?

----------------

UPDATE SEPTEMBER 14, 2013 !!!

COLLABORATION WITH BROKENDECK (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/3985589/)

The user brokendeck has cleaned up the mod so that it adds the three rooms, but doesn\'t alter the vanilla Sky Haven Temple. Originally having done this on his own so that he could repair and use my mod with his own SHT mod, he thought that other users would probably want this sort of compatibility as well. The Sanctuarium is now accessible from the hallway just to the right as you go up the left-side stairs towards the sleeping area. A newly created door is now the entrance. Many of the lighting bugs have also been fixed and the Sanctuarium is altogether brighter.

----------------


This mod contains:

- The room \"Sky Haven Sanctuarium\" (accessible via the Temple), contains shrines, an alchemy/enchantment alcove, an intelligence-alcove, a small infirmary and a small library)
- The room \"Sky Haven Citadel\" (accessible via the Sanctuarium)
- The room \"Sky Haven Thermal Bath\" (accessible via the Sanctuarium, contains only a bathing area for your character - for now)
- \"Jena Maximus\", a Blade NPC so the place doesn\'t look completely bereft of life.

----------------

Additional notes:
I am a total noob in modding and although I\'ve put much effort into this (and will) there is a high possibility that this does not work the way you want it to. I\'d be very thankful to receive feedback and suggestions on this beta in the comments-section or via pm.
I am also not a native English speaker and therefore prone to mistakes concerning the English language. If you find mistakes, please take a minute and inform me. I want to become better!
author: MHGhandi and brokendeck
